# Under the Sea 2026  
**Turku Riichi-mahjong club Nagashi ry will organize “Under the Sea 2026” tournament on 24.10. - 25.10. in T-Talo.**   
During the two days eight hachans will be played.  
The time limit for each hanchan is 90 minutes.  
The tournament is played using EMA rules and the tournament results will be recorded in the National MFRS rankings and the EMA MERS rankings.  
Latest EMA rules will be used and you can find the current active EMA rules 2025 [here](http://mahjong-europe.org/portal/images/docs/Riichi-rules-2025-EN.pdf)   


The tournament will be held on the 24th and 25th of October at [T-Talo](https://maps.app.goo.gl/z8gytuZadcxEGpTd9), which is located near the Turku University Hospital at street 'Vanha Hämeentie 29', 20540 Turku.   


The tournament fee is €20 for Nagashi ry members and €25 for non-members. You can also become a member of Nagashi for €5, in which case the amount of membership + tournament fee is €25 in total. 
The membership is valid until the end of 2027. You can become a member regardless of your place of residence. 
The tournament and the membership fee can be paid by bank transfer or in cash or credit card at the beginning of the event.  
Tournament fees paid by bank transfer must be completed by October 17th. Otherwise, you must be able to show a receipt for the bank transfer on the spot.   

